{
  "stem": "20142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somehow we had-- we had some gasoline and we had naphtha.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Naphtha was a-- a byproduct of oil that was a cooking-- for cooking purposes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was quite a little bit available for it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in every bunker they had canisters of such material for cooking purposes and for creating-- building, making bombs.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a-- we-- I-- I was given a gun that I would say did not fire quite well, because I couldn't tell if I really hit anybody or-- and-- but I was aiming quite well.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was sure that it will come to good use.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ammunition was made by a girl sitting in a-- in the bunkers and preparing, pouring-- pouring lead into a certain form.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The lead, we had quite a bit of it from previously [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] collected by the leaders of the preparation for the uprising.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would like to mention to you that during the January 6, there were some girls with us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one of them, [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hella, ?] had a gun in her hand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Germans were all screaming, they have-- Jews have arms and women are shooting at us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's sounded in German that-- like this, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was a sound that we are very, very proud of, because we couldn't imagine that Germans could actually recognize such things as the fact that the women are fighting alongside of us, just as the children, they were fighting with us.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they were hit in the helmets and they dropped the guns and they raised their hands and asking for-- for mercy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's when they started to scream, the Jews, Jews have the weapons and the women are-- are shooting at them.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
